Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:37.60,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,开启故事之门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:40.37,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,用持有的钥匙  被选择的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:42.54,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:05.88,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,救救这个世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.09,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,让我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:11.47,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:13.20,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:16.63,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:25.28,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:26.62,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:31.77,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,开启故事之门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:34.17,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,用持有的钥匙  被选择的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.61,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那么你也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:37.06,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,和妹妹...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:39.18,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,对了  绮罗叶呢？
