Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:56.29,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:58.94,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好像拿着什么好东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:13.07,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那个...谢谢
