Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.08,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,想到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:39.59,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:40.21,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,就是这样
