Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:41.92,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:44.20,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:50.88,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,总之就拜托说谎的手臂了
