Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:11.82,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,最讨厌！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:12.50,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,最讨厌！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:13.49,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,最讨厌！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:19.25,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,最最最最最最...最讨厌了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.49,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,成功了
