Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:39.87,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大家当心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:50.68,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,总算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:52.80,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大成功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:56.33,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,绮罗叶真是好厉害哦
