Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:03.57,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,雾香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:05.59,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你们好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:11.62,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,哦
